                      </div>
                    <div class="media-body">
                      <p >Official images of the three sets based on Captain America: Civil War have been released on a Polish LEGO website: extraklocki.pl. The images are fairly low resolution so I am not going to upload them to Brickset for the time being but you can view them all here. Watch out for a potential spoiler.<br>
                      They look great to me and I can hardly wait for them to be released in March! We will, of course, be reviewing them all closer to their release date.
                      </p>    
